title: European cities ranked worst for over-tourism 2017
summary: This bar chart has 10 columns on the x axis representing Tourist Places, and Overtourism score (1-10) in each Tourist Places on the y axis.
The Overtourism score (1-10) is appeared to be the highest at Tourist Places Nantes France and lowest at Tourist Places Barcelona Spain.
The difference of Overtourism score (1-10) between the highest and lowest Tourist Places is 1.56.
